author: cbs8
title: FCA to Announce Third Quarter 2015 Financial Results on October 28
text:
Fiat Chrysler Automobiles
LONDON , October 16,
Fiat Chrysler Automobiles N.V. (NYSE: FCAU / MI: FCA) announced today that its financial results for the third quarter of 2015 will be released on Wednesday, October 28, 2015 .
A live audio webcast of the 2015 Q3 results conference call will begin at 4.00 p.m. GMT / 5.00 p.m. CET / 12.00 p.m. EDT on Wednesday, October 28 .
Details for accessing this presentation are available in the Investors section of the Group's website at http://www.fcagroup.com . For those unable to participate in the live session, a replay will remain archived on the corporate website ( http://www.fcagroup.com ) for two weeks after the call.
